title: Domestic beer consumption in Canada by age group 2019
summary: Overall Share of beer consumption has increased over the Year.
Share of beer consumption is slightly increasing from 12_to_17 to 18_to_34, and finally roughly constant from 18_to_34 to 50_to_64.
The line rapidly increased by 3770.0% from Year 12_to_17 to 18_to_34.
The steepest increase occurs in between the Year 12_to_17 and 18_to_34.
The highest Share of beer consumption, of value 38.7 was reached at Year 18_to_34
The lowest Share of beer consumption, of value 1.0 was reported at Year 12_to_17
